Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:08.52,main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what the king has been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:13.53,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,Malty-sama must've talked him into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.99,main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,How is the Shield Hero holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:20.70,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,He procured a demi-human \Ngirl from a slave trader.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:23.16,main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:26.17,main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.17,main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:30.92,main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,News of Melromarc's summoning \Nof the Four Cardinal Heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:33.80,main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,is making waves here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:39.14,main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,We must prevent our neighbors \Nfrom meddling, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:44.14,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,We'll continue to keep an eye \Non things in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:45.60,main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:05.12,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,As a reward for your efforts during the \NWave and for fulfilling my request,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:07.62,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-dono will receive 4,000 silvers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:13.88,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,and Itsuki-dono and Ren-dono \Nwill receive 3,800.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:18.30,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,And as agreed upon, I have set \Naside 500 silvers for the Shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:19.39,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:24.14,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's offset by the cost of \Nfreeing his slave from her curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.56,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,he will receive no funds this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:30.48,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's going to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.74,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,You interfered in his duel, dispelled the...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:37.53,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,slave crest, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:41.53,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,And now you refuse to pay \Nhim what he deserves?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.62,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.87,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd followed the rules, \NNaofumi clearly would've won that duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:48.57,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... I didn't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:52.54,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken, Itsuki-sama, Ren-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:54.46,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,It was a one-on-one duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:58.18,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,and the Shield Hero was the one \Nwith monsters hidden in his cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:01.89,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,That is why Father didn't \Ndeclare him the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:05.06,top,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, you cheated by \Nfiring a magic spell at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.77,flashback,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.36,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cowardly cheat, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.99,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, when the Wave hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:26.95,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,it was Naofumi who defended that \Nvillage in the knights' stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:34.00,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he must be \Ncompensated in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:39.76,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I shall afford him \Nthe minimum agreed amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.85,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,You have it, so begone already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.73,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:52.98,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to waste our \Ntime in this place anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.27,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,645)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:45.93,sign_6743_43_Filo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(438,596)}Filo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:50.91,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:54.27,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,She now has a new slave crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There was no need to get \Nanother one, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:01.36,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted it, as a symbol \Nof your faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.91,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.99,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Slave User's Shield, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.38,sign_9442_51_Slave_User_s_Shi,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,268)}Slave User's Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.42,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:28.26,top,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you helped that scrawny bag of \Nbones grow so much in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.01,top,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's not a virgin, she's guaranteed\N to fetch you twenty gold pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.60,top,R,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} a virgin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.10,top,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-five, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-five gold pieces, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.77,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.32,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,A monster egg lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.20,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Pay 100 silvers, and you're \Nguaranteed at least a filolial!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:51.33,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,You'll win a monster chick that'll \Ndouble in value if you raise it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A filolial?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.54,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You must've seen them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:59.50,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,They're the large birds that pull \Ncarriages around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.17,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, if you hit the jackpot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:12.14,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,you'll win a dragon worth twenty gold pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.76,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What, it's like a gacha game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.27,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What's a gacha game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.65,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:24.65,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Act now, and I'll give you a package \Ndeal for that and the slave crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.86,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't waste money \Nlike that, Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:34.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I figured it wouldn't be fair \Nto make you fight alone all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A monster should at least be some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can fight by myself just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:43.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If so, we can just sell it \Nback to the slave trader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:48.59,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, don't loosen your \Npurse strings any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:55.51,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,Relatives of mine in Lute Village \Nasked me to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.56,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Think it was someone you saved back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:04.44,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,This book has recipes for finer \Nmedicines than you bring to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.61,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,Use it. It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.40,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I can't read this \Nworld's language, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.53,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.12,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,The old hag at the magic \Nshop wants to see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.49,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,It's for a similar reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.33,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,She said you helped her \Ngrandkid out in Lute Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:24.29,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,You have an affinity for healing \Nand support magic, Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.76,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,And the young lady has \Nlight and dark magic affinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.13,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,She is half-raccoon, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.47,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend she learn illusion \Nmagic and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.22,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,In which case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the money \Nto buy a magic grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.02,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,It's free, as thanks for \Nhelping my grandkid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:49.36,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,I actually would've loved to give \Nyou a crystal ball instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.65,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:56.58,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,If you use a crystal ball, you can \Nlearn one of the magics sealed in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,First I've heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:03.25,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard the royal court ordered a \Nbunch of them for the heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they handed them \Nout to every hero but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.88,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,Learning magic from a grimoire is hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:14.26,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,but if you keep at it, you can \Nlearn as many spells as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.26,main,OldMag,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.02,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:31.11,top,N,0000,0000,0000,,I wish there was a skill that'd \Ntranslate books for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.70,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Let's learn together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What? The language and magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.70,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:42.79,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But the key word there is "together."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:47.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There's more than a month \Nuntil the next Wave,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:48.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess there's no better plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's spend the night in Lute Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And tomorrow, we can go grind \Nsome levels after breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:05.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:27.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute, Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:32.17,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It must think you're its mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Imprinting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We should think of a good name for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:28.85,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she grew \Nso much in just two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.36,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,My Growth Boost skill probably helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:31.56,sign_16939_131_Monster_Tamer_s_,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Mon
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:31.61,sign_16939_131_Monster_Tamer_s_,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:31.65,sign_16939_131_Monster_Tamer_s_,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Tam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:31.69,sign_16939_131_Monster_Tamer_s_,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Tamer's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:31.73,sign_16939_131_Monster_Tamer_s_,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Tamer's Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.27,sign_16939_131_Monster_Tamer_s_,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Tamer's Shield III
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:38.24,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You named her Filo? As in "filolial"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.82,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's a bit lazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to like it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.58,main,G1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.79,main,G2,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the knights here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:55.30,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,In light of his exploits during the last Wave,\N the Spear Hero, Motoyasu-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.88,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,has been appointed ruling lord of this region.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.18,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,To help the rebuilding efforts, \Nwe've decided to levy a toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:08.10,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty silvers to enter the village,\N and fifty to exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.19,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.65,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We won't even have anything to eat tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.19,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to defy your lord's orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.19,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:21.11,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,You were still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.99,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,This is Motoyasu-sama's domain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.62,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to question him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:29.00,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, get out this instant,\N criminal scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:35.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind leaving, but I don't think \Nthe villagers are gonna accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:39.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu, do you know how much it costs \Nto spend a night at the inn here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.72,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's one silver a night, food included.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:49.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're charging a hundred nights' worth of\Nmoney just to enter and exit the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.06,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:51.81,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:54.61,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you can't just show \Nup and call yourself our lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:58.44,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,And it was the Shield Hero who defended \Nthis village during the Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:01.28,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,You dare complain about a royal decree?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You people had better knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:13.42,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you know who we are, Malty-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.38,main,Malty,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:17.84,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.22,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No idea, but I can tell they're important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.43,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,How could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.22,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.06,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Fight us for the right to rule this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:41.61,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,But if we lose this, the village will \Nfall into the Spear Hero's hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:47.12,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,As the current lord, even I cannot \Naccept further taxation at this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:52.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But why does that mean I have to take part\N in a dragon race? It sounds like a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.79,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,They've asked for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.88,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, we don't have the \Nright to challenge a Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:03.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That letter probably said \Nsomething Myne didn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.72,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So she challenged you to take it out on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:14.06,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,Your filolial seems to be up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:21.53,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So it's true that filolials \Nand dragons don't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.49,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,Please, we beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.53,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,We promise you a reward for winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.24,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not responsible for what \Nhappens if I lose, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.96,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,So lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.59,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,And it's a bird, not a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:45.17,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna race my dragon with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.18,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.19,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.94,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Healing magic! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.40,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is definitely going to bruise...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.86,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.48,top,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,You cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault for getting too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:12.16,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Naofumi-sama\Nsmile so much before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.87,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,The course will be three laps around \Nthe outskirts of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:20.58,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever reaches this gate first \Nwill be declared the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.50,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.88,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,On your marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.18,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.58,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,As source of thy power, I order thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:59.75,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of nature and \Ncreate a pit in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.00,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.84,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,No! The Shield Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.26,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.22,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.56,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.40,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,As source of thy power, I order thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.91,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of nature \Nand slow my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.32,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Speed Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.08,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:38.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.73,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Run faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.40,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo! One last lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.36,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Accursed beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:17.12,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of nature \Nand hasten my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.12,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Fast Speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.46,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,He's blocking my path!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.92,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading straight for the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:58.95,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.20,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Shield Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.66,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.83,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him beat you! Keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We won, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:25.14,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliantly done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:28.81,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can rest easy and focus \Non rebuilding the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.94,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna thank someone, thank Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.29,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,You cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:46.42,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell us your filolial \Nwas really this massive tub of lard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:49.92,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,But it only transformed \Nafter the race was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.30,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Making holes and all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.22,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Holes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:57.68,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.01,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:04.06,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,We detected traces of magic on the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.52,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was that criminal, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.78,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,No. The Shield Hero's magic affinities \Nare healing and support.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:15.11,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,His raccoon friend's are light and dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.78,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,Completely different types \Nthan the magic we found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.41,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,When did they learn so much about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:24.12,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear that the \NSpear Hero's party cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:28.00,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine! We shall leave for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.75,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I let you win today,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.88,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,but it won't happen next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.88,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, this fatso...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is your crotch okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:44.97,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, just you wait! \NI'll get you yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.94,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:56.03,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero, again, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:59.61,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know how to express our \Ngratitude for everything you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:05.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that. Hand over the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:09.71,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,We're going around the village \Ncollecting money now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.29,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us a few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.21,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:20.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want rumors spreading about\N how I took all your rebuilding funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.97,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody in this village would ever say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:30.06,main,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,But then, what else can we give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:51.12,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Naofumi-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,but could we stop for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:11.98,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you do this after \Nyou let me rest on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll mostly be traveling by carriage now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:18.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You should try to get over \Nyour motion sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:19.19,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is a little red.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:22.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.11,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo looks happy now that she \Ngets to draw a carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.20,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,She sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.34,flashback,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in becoming \Na traveling trader, Sir Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:37.42,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,A traveling trader?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.80,flashback,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,If so, this pass will come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:46.30,flashback,Lord,0000,0000,0000,,It exempts you from tolls across the country,\Nso you can traverse the roads as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:51.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We can run a traveling business while \Nfighting monsters and leveling up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:52.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.85,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just sleep for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:57.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.40,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.32,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Your feathers are stuffy as hell, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:18.04,main,Filo,0000,0000,0000,,Meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.84,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama... Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:31.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I must've fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:44.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.49,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:56.34,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:57.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ma—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:59.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:04.39,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:40.01,sign_81788_789_Walking_Over_Cor,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(356,1)}A New Comrade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:42.01,sign_81788_789_Walking_Over_Cor,,0000,0000,0000,,
